    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited as a project car or for parts. The engine currently runs very roughly and has several significant fluid leaks that require immediate attention before it can be considered roadworthy. Externally, the body shows considerable wear with visible rust on the rocker panels and various dents and scratches throughout. The interior is also in rough shape, with torn upholstery and some non-functional electronics. Please expect to invest significant time and money into repairs if you plan to get this back on the road.",
