      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 12
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a collector-grade E92 M3, featuring the legendary S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8 with its signature 8,400 RPM redline and individual throttle bodies. This specimen exhibits flawless Alpine White paint and an immaculate interior, reflecting a life of climate-controlled storage. Mechanically, the vehicle is superlative; the M-DCT dual-clutch transmission delivers crisp, millisecond shifts, while the Electronic Damper Control (EDC) provides precise chassis tuning. Crucially, the rod bearings and throttle actuators have been addressed preventatively with documented proof. With zero track history and a completely stock configuration, this is a rare opportunity to own a pristine example of the final naturally aspirated M3.",
